{
  "stem": "13141.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- the next day, in fact, I stayed with a cousin of mine, once removed, with my mother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lived in Long Island, in Woodmere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I worked in his business-- the next day, he took me right to his business and on the Long Island Railroad, and then the subway in Pennsylvania Station, and then going to-- on the subway to his business.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there I worked as a stock clerk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I took the packages to the post office with the little push cart.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after about-- I did that for about two weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He told me he was going on a vacation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt-- I mean, I would have stayed there all by myself at the house, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my English wasn't too good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I spoke English because I had learned English before, but it wasn't too good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I just felt I had an inkling that he wasn't too keen that I would stay at the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he said, maybe you want to look around, you know, for a room or some place to live, maybe with a friend in Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I must say that I made only $8.40 a week at the time, so I couldn't get very far.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the day before he left on vacation, I said also goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went with my two suitcases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went to Manhattan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And took the suitcases first to the place where I worked, and then after hours-- at the time you still worked 48 hours-- and then after hours, I went with my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had called a friend of mine who had given-- who was one of the two who had given the $120 for my passage.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
